      "raw_text": "A. NJ. Macho, an employcmtn agent,\nsenior partner in the firm of Macho l.\nDavis, with an office at 2l4 Stevens\nstreet, was arrested this morning by\nOfficer Burns on a warrant charging\nhim with violating city ordinance\nA2sS, which refers to employment\nagencies. The warrant was sworn out\nby A. Meadows. He alleges that he\npaid fee to Macho and in return was\nto be sent with his wife to a ranch."
